tool_description: An unofficial API showing Arsenal FC latest men's, women's players and also latest club news.
name: Arsenal FC
title: Arsenal FC

api_list.name: Get Arsenal FC latest news
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://arsenal-fc.p.rapidapi.com/news"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "arsenal-fc.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
